  "text": "Proof. 2. Using [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] one can show g(λ n ) = 1. Hence the highest weight vector f ∈ O(W ) of weight λ n is uniquely determined up to a scalar. We explicitly constructed f and (guided by computer calculations) proved that f ( n, n, n ) = 0. Hence λ n ∈ S( n, n, n ).",
